{"word":"G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee - Boast","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καυχάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kaucháomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kow-khah'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Boast"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மேன்மைபாராட்டு, பெருமைபாராட்டு, புகழ்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to glory (whether with reason or without): absolutely"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From some (obsolete) base akin to that of <b>&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>aucheo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>boast</i>) and <a href=\"#/G2172 - εὔχομαι - eúchomai - yoo'-khom-ahee/2172\">G2172</a>; to <i>vaunt</i> (in a good or a bad sense): - (make) boast, glory, joy, rejoice."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2620 - κατακαυχάομαι - katakaucháomai - kat-ak-ow-khah'-om-ahee/2620\">G2620</a>, <a href=\"#/G2744 - καυχάομαι - kaucháomai - kow-khah'-om-ahee/2744\">G2744</a>, <a href=\"#/G2745 - καύχημα - kaúchēma - kow'-khay-mah/2745\">G2745</a>, <a href=\"#/G2746 - καύχησις - kaúchēsis - kow'-khay-sis/2746\">G2746</a>"}]}